</div>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#777"># –≤—ã–≤–µ—Å—Ç–∏ –Ω–∞ —ç–∫—Ä–∞–Ω –ø–∞—Ä–æ–ª–∏ –¥–ª–∏–Ω–æ–π 6 —Å–∏–º–≤–æ–ª–æ–≤</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span><span style="color:#777"># –∑–∞–ø–∏—Å–∞—Ç—å —ç—Ç–æ –≤ –æ—Ç–¥–µ–ª—å–Ω—ã–π —Ñ–∞–π–ª</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>input = <span style="color:#036;font-weight:bold">File</span>.open(<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">password_2.txt</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>, <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">r</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>)
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span><span style="color:#777"># Enter your password</span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span>print <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Enter your password: </span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n8" name="n8">8</a></span>password = gets.strip
<span class="line-numbers"> <a href="#n9" name="n9">9</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><strong><a href="#n10" name="n10">10</a></strong></span><span style="color:#777"># Your password is weak / not weak</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n11" name="n11">11</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">while</span> (line = input.gets)
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n12" name="n12">12</a></span>  line.strip!
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n13" name="n13">13</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n14" name="n14">14</a></span>  <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">if</span> line == password
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n15" name="n15">15</a></span>    puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Your password is weak!</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n16" name="n16">16</a></span>    exit
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n17" name="n17">17</a></span>  <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n18" name="n18">18</a></span><span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">end</span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n19" name="n19">19</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><strong><a href="#n20" name="n20">20</a></strong></span>puts <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">Your password is hard!</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n21" name="n21">21</a></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n22" name="n22">22</a></span>input.close
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<p>GET - –ø–æ–ª—É—á–∏—Ç—å (–±—Ä–∞—É–∑–µ—Ä)
POST - –æ—Ç–ø—Ä–∞–≤–∏—Ç—å (–±—Ä–∞—É–∑–µ—Ä)</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>–ò–∑—É—á–∏ —Å—Å—ã–ª–∫—É: RFC HTTP
 http://lib.ru/WEBMASTER/rfc2068/</p>
</blockquote>

